    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Taijutsu (Strike)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 7</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 8</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 21 | <b>Successes:</b> 3</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 9 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 22</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> None</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>This technique functions as Gouken: Taihouken, except as above, and the bonus damage becomes 3d6, plus 1d6 per 4 levels (up to 8d6 total bonus damage). On a failed save, the target is knocked back 20 ft and falls @Condition[prone]{prone}. You suffer a -4 penalty to Learn checks when learning this technique if you do not have the Gouken feat.</p>\n\n\n\n",
